Class HttpMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.http.javadsl.model.HttpMethod
      • akka.http.scaladsl.model.HttpMethod
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Renderable, SingletonValueRenderable, java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product

    public final class HttpMethod
extends HttpMethod
implements SingletonValueRenderable, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    The method of an HTTP request. param: isSafe true if the resource should not be altered on the server param: isIdempotent true if requests can be safely (& automatically) repeated param: requestEntityAcceptance Expected if meaning of request entities is properly defined
